          ],
          "params": [],
          "returnType": null,
          "description": "Maps to ConvolverNode.normalize. When true the browser applies an equal-power normalization pass on the IR so different IRs play at a consistent perceived loudness. Default true (the Web Audio spec default). **Note:** the Web Audio spec only respects normalize if it is set *before* buffer is assigned. This class always writes normalize first. Changing normalize at runtime while an IR is loaded re-assigns the buffer so the new value takes effect."
        },
